---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SectionHeader from '../components/SectionHeader.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | TechSoft Systems"
  description="About Jonathan (John) and TechSoft Systems private AI and infrastructure practice."
>
  <section class="pt-12">
    <SectionHeader title="About" subtitle="TechSoft Systems is led by Jonathan (John), focused on private AI and resilient infrastructure delivery." />

    <div class="mt-8 rounded-3xl border border-zinc-300/50 bg-white/80 p-8 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5">
      <p class="text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
        Jonathan (John) helps organizations build and run secure infrastructure and private AI systems that can survive real operational pressure.
        The work spans architecture design, migrations, reliability programs, and team training with a strong emphasis on practicality.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
        Core focus areas include containerized workloads, GPU-backed inference stacks, observability, and compliance-aware operations.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
